text: Ilona Szöllõsi (born 2 July 1908, date of death unknown) was a Hungarian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Hungarian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
